{
  "texts": [
    "Since the current study adopted mature scales from foreign research, in order to avoid interpretation biases caused by language and understanding differences.",
    "The foreign scales were translated in both directions by two master's students and one international student and then reviewed and adjusted by the project team through discussions.",
    "The initial questionnaire underwent multiple trial fills and modifications to finally form the official questionnaire, which contains 12 measurement dimensions and 44 measurement items, as shown in Table 2.",
    "This study utilized a questionnaire survey method to randomly gather data from Generation Z consumers with purchase intentions and purchasing power.",
    "The data collection period was from June 2023 to July 2023."
  ]
}